OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FA train driver was killed and dozens
OL,7,Fof others were seriously injured when
OL,8,Ftwo passenger trains collided near
OL,9,FBedford, an ambulance service said.
OL,11,FFootage from the aftermath shows the
OL,12,Fincident involved two East Midlands
OL,13,FRailway (EMR) services, with one
OL,14,Fsmashing into the back of the other on
OL,15,Fthe same line shortly after 5pm on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FA passenger on board one of the trains
OL,19,Freported being "flung into the chair
OL,20,Fin front, and then I saw smoke".
OL,26,@{D@POU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
