OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FOne person died, 11 suffered "very
OL,7,Fserious" injuries and 22 were
OL,8,Fseriously injured, East of England
OL,9,FAmbulance Service said.
OL,11,FDave Calfe, general secretary of Aslef
OL,12,Fthe train drivers' union, said: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts tonight are with the family
OL,14,Fand friends of the driver who died in
OL,15,Fthe crash near Bedford today and with
OL,16,Fthe passengers who were injured in the
OL,17,Faccident. We want to thank the
OL,18,Femergency services who responded so
OL,19,Fquickly, to help those on board, and
OL,20,Fare still at the scene."
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@HO]tD@aOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FAll patients with the most serious
OL,7,Finjuries have all now been taken to
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FA further 56 people sustained minor
OL,11,Finjuries and were treated at the scene
OL,12,For in hospital.
OL,14,FMost carriages of the two southbound
OL,15,Ftrains remained on the tracks but at
OL,16,Fleast one derailed.
OL,18,FThe two trains involved were operating
OL,19,Fthe 4.40pm departure from Corby and
OL,20,Fthe 3.50pm departure from Nottingham,
OL,21,Fboth to London St Pancras.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
