OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FAir ambulance helicopters were on the
OL,7,Fground after the collision happened
OL,8,Fjust south of the Elstow interchange
OL,9,Fbetween the A421 and the A6.
OL,11,FThere was a long line of emergency
OL,12,Fvehicles on a rural road as emergency
OL,13,Fcrews and passengers gathered in a
OL,14,Fneighbouring field.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
