PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FMembers of the public were asked to
OL,7,Favoid the scene of the crash, while
OL,8,FBedford Hospital and Luton and
OL,9,FDunstable University Hospital both
OL,10,Fasked people not to attend their
OL,11,Femergency departments "unless they
OL,12,Fhave a genuine medical emergency" as
OL,13,Fthey responded to the incident.
OL,15,FEMR trains to and from the London were
OL,16,Fsuspended for the rest of the day.
OL,26,@sD@WOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
