PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FOnline train trackers show the rolling
OL,7,Fstock involved in the crash were a
OL,8,Fclass 360 and class 810, with the
OL,9,Ffront of the former hitting the rear
OL,10,Fof the latter.
OL,12,FEMR began rolling out class 810s in
OL,13,FDecember last year, while class 360s
OL,14,Fare at least 20 years old.
OL,16,FRail journalist Tony Miles said the
OL,17,Fcrash appears to have been a
OL,18,F"relatively slow speed collision".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
