PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FHe told Sky News: "Obviously it's a
OL,7,Frear end collision, they were going in
OL,8,Fthe same direction, so one of them,
OL,9,Fthe rear one was going faster than the
OL,10,Fone it's caught up with, for some
OL,11,Freason. That's not a complicated
OL,12,Fassumption.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
