FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,F"So, the question has to be how has
OL,7,Fthat train that's in the rear got into
OL,8,Fcontact with the train that it was
OL,9,Ffollowing, and obviously it's either
OL,10,Fgone past the signal that was telling
OL,11,Fit it should stop, or the signal was
OL,12,Ffaulty, or the driver's made a mistake
OL,13,Fin some way, or didn't read the
OL,14,Fsignal, or something."
OL,16,FHe added: "Even if you're going 40
OL,17,Fmiles an hour and you come to a halt
OL,18,Fin a few metres, you've got the energy
OL,19,Fof a 40-mile-an-hour body in you, and
OL,20,Fyou're going to move until you hit
OL,21,Fsomething, unfortunately.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@VO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
