OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,F"So, even relatively low-speed
OL,7,Fcollisions can be dangerous for people
OL,8,Fthat are on board."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Network Rail, which
OL,11,Fmanages Britain's rail infrastructure,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are supporting the efforts
OL,13,Fof emergency services on scene and our
OL,14,Fthoughts are with everyone involved."
OL,16,FA team of Rail Accident Investigation
OL,17,FBranch inspectors is on site to gather
OL,18,Fevidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]tD@GOUvD@eO]
