OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781918292
OL,3,COne dead and dozens seriously injured
OL,4,Cas two trains collide near Bedford
OL,6,FThe crash follows a collision between
OL,7,Ftwo trains in mid Wales in October
OL,8,F2024 in which one passenger died and
OL,9,Ffour other people were seriously hurt.
OL,11,FThat was Britain's first fatal crash
OL,12,Finvolving multiple trains for more
OL,13,Fthan a quarter of a century.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
